Part 2 - the details 

When we create for a client, we aren’t just tapping into imagery that they love from other weddings but approaching the process in a custom direction. Pulling imagery from fashion, interior design, nature, and imagery that encompasses a feeling. 

Samantha, our beautiful bride, wanted transition their wedding plans from a 170 guest count to 50 and invite all into their beautiful home. Leaning into the details of their home and incorporating this extension into their backyard. From incorporating the @haydesign pendants over their tablescape to colors and textures from their landscaping into the florals, each element was thoughtfully curated as we leaned into the space and overall feel of their home. 

Captured @kristenmarieparker
